edlab.eda.transistorModel

Class TransistorModelMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • edlab.eda.transistorModel.TransistorModelMetaData

  • public class TransistorModelMetaData
extends java.lang.Object
    A class used to house relevant MetaData for a transistor model. The given example parses the data from a specific format in a csv file, however if other input methods are desired for metaData that can be accomplished by adding additional constructors
